*-----------------------------------
* Allergy Matrix Requirements Draft
*-----------------------------------
  - Allergy matrix source = provided Baja Cantina allergy matrix and banquet allergy replacement sheets
  - The app should model allergens as structured fields for each menu item
  - The app should show whether an item contains an allergen, can be modified, or has a recommended replacement
  - Matrix colour logic should be represented in data rather than relying only on colour
  - Status values should include Safe, Contains, Modification Available, Not Suitable, May Contain, Requires Confirmation
  - The app should not use colour alone for allergen safety; text labels are required
  - Banquet allergy replacements should be searchable and available as a separate staff reference mode

*------------------------------
* Allergy Matrix Fields Draft
*------------------------------
  - Food Item
  - Section
  - Meat
  - Seafood
  - Crustacean
  - Sulphites
  - Vegetarian
  - Vegan
  - Gluten
  - Sesame
  - Tree Nuts
  - Dairy
  - Raw
  - Onion Family
  - Chilli
  - Egg
  - Soy
  - MSG
  - Coriander
  - Modification Notes
  - Replacement Suggestion
  - Coeliac Suitability
  - Cross Contamination Risk
  - Requires Manager Confirmation

*--------------------------------------
* Allergy Replacement Rules Draft
*--------------------------------------
  - Mix Dips
      - Vegan Issue = Requires replacement or removal
      - Sesame Modification = No macha sauce
      - Dairy Replacement = Wings 3 pieces where visible in provided sheet
      - Chilli Modification = No salsa fresca; no macha sauce
      - Coriander Replacement = Tuna tostada or no coriander depending banquet sheet context

  - Burrata
      - Sesame Modification = No macha sauce
      - Replacement Suggestion = Tuna tartare where visible in Suprema sheet

  - Corn Ribs
      - Sesame Modification = No macha sauce
      - Chilli Modification = No macha, no chipotle where visible

  - Ceviche / Tuna
      - Vegetarian Replacement = Rajas quesadilla frita / rajas option where visible
      - Raw Replacement = Rajas quesadilla frita / rajas option where visible
      - Chilli Modification = No chilli
      - Coriander Modification = No coriander

  - Wagyu Taco
      - Meat Replacement = Cauliflower or Baja where visible
      - Vegetarian Replacement = Cauliflower / Baja option where visible
      - Gluten Replacement = Corn tortilla
      - Dairy Modification = No cheese
      - Raw Modification = Well done
      - Chilli Modification = No chipotle / no salsa depending banquet sheet context
      - Coriander Modification = No coriander / no avo mousse where visible

  - Baja Fish / Prawn
      - Seafood Replacement = Fish taco or fish alternative where visible
      - Crustacean Replacement = Fish or cauliflower where visible
      - Vegetarian Replacement = Cauliflower
      - Gluten Replacement = Corn tortilla

  - Grilled King Prawn
      - Seafood Replacement = Wagyu taco where visible
      - Crustacean Replacement = Wagyu taco where visible
      - Vegetarian Replacement = Corn ribs or Baja cauliflower / vegetarian taco option where visible
      - Chilli Modification = No chilli; no chipotle mayo

  - Quesadilla Frita Chorizo
      - Meat Replacement = Quesadilla prawn or veggie where visible
      - Vegetarian Replacement = Enchilada / Suiza where visible
      - Gluten Status = Cross-contamination requires confirmation
      - Dairy Replacement = Beef taco where visible
      - Chilli Replacement = Cheese quesadilla where visible
      - Coriander Modification = No coriander

  - Quesadilla Frita Rajas
      - Gluten Status = Cross-contamination requires confirmation
      - Dairy Replacement = Chicken taco where visible
      - Coriander Modification = No guac where visible

  - Lamb
      - Meat Replacement = Fish / prawns where visible
      - Vegetarian Replacement = Fajitas vegetarian where visible
      - Dairy Replacement = Central dessert dairy free option where visible
      - Chilli Replacement = Wagyu tacos no salsa where visible
      - Coriander Modification = No coriander

  - Churros
      - Dairy Replacement = Flan or Mangoyada where visible
      - Tree Nuts Status = May contain
      - Soy Replacement = Mangoyada / Paleta where visible

  - Chocolate Tart
      - Dairy Replacement = Mangoyada where visible
      - Tree Nuts Status = Contains or may contain nuts praline; requires confirmation
      - Soy Replacement = Flan or alternative where visible

  - Flan
      - Dairy Replacement = Paleta where visible

